{
  "texts": [
    "Optionally, users can query the model for additional details using prompts such as \"The tumor thickness is\", and the model will complete the sentence, e.g., \"The tumor thickness is 1.2 mm\".",
    "b We train HistoGPT in two phases.",
    "In the first phase, the vision module of HistoGPT is pre-trained using multiple instance learning (MIL).",
    "In the second phase, we freeze the pre-trained layers and fine-tune the language module on the image-text pairs.",
    "To prevent the model from overfitting on the same sentences, we apply text augmentation with GPT-4 to paraphrase the original reports."
  ]
}